OL,3,CNew wild swimming spots will be
OL,4,Cmonitored to ensure water safety
OL,6,FIt brings the total number of sites
OL,7,Ffor the 2024 water bathing season
OL,8,Fbetween May 15 and September 30 to 451
OL,9,Facross England.
OL,11,FIt comes after growing public anger
OL,12,Fover the state of England's rivers and
OL,13,Fcoastal waters, which suffer pollution
OL,14,Ffrom sewage outlets and other sources
OL,15,Fsuch as agricultural run-off.
OL,17,FDespite this, according to Defra, last
OL,18,Fyear 96% of bathing waters in England
OL,19,Fmet minimum annual standards and 90%
OL,20,Fwere rated as "good" or "excellent".
