OL,3,CNew wild swimming spots will be
OL,4,Cmonitored to ensure water safety
OL,6,FDefra said the Government will also be
OL,7,Flaunching a consultation later this
OL,8,Fyear on proposals to reform bathing
OL,9,Fwater regulations in England.
OL,11,FThis includes proposed change to drive
OL,12,Fimprovements to water quality at
OL,13,Fbathing spots, enhance monitoring and
OL,14,Fenable more flexibility around the
OL,15,Fdates of the monitoring season.
