OL,6,FThe Government will seek public and
OL,7,Fstakeholder views on extending the
OL,8,Fdefinition of "bathers" to include a
OL,9,Fwider range of water users beyond
OL,10,Fswimmers ` such as rowers, kayakers
OL,11,Fand paddle boarders.
OL,13,FMaking the announcement on what was
OL,14,Fdescribed as the "largest ever
OL,15,Frollout" of new bathing sites, water
OL,16,Fminister Robbie Moore says he's
OL,17,Fpleased to have approved "a further 27
OL,18,Fnew bathing water sites".
