OL,6,FMr Moore said: "The value our bathing
OL,7,Fwaters bring to local communities is
OL,8,Fincredibly valuable ` providing
OL,9,Fsocial, physical and positive health
OL,10,Fand wellbeing benefits to people
OL,11,Faround the country.
OL,13,F"I am fully committed to seeing the
OL,14,Fquality of our coastal waters, rivers
OL,15,Fand lakes rise further for the benefit
OL,16,Fof the environment and everyone who
OL,17,Fuses them."
