OL,3,CNew wild swimming spots will be
OL,4,Cmonitored to ensure water safety
OL,6,FAlan Lovell, Environment Agency
OL,7,Fchairman, said: "Overall bathing water
OL,8,Fquality has improved massively over
OL,9,Fthe last decade due to targeted and
OL,10,Frobust regulation from the Environment
OL,11,FAgency, and the good work carried out
OL,12,Fby partners and local groups.
OL,14,F"We know that improvements can take
OL,15,Ftime and investment from the water
OL,16,Findustry, farmers and local
OL,17,Fcommunities, but where the investment
OL,18,Fis made, standards can improve."
